31	//! this module is `unsafe` today â€” `objc2-app-kit`'s `generalPasteboard`,
32	//! `pasteboardItems`, `NSPasteboardItem::types`, and `dataForType` are all
33	//! safe wrappers in 0.3.2. If a future refactor needs raw pointer access
34	//! (e.g. to avoid a byte-vec copy), keep the `unsafe` block inside this
